These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-1::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, pall-mall, tiparillo
1. the tiparillo-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
2. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2   |   3    |
| Cigar   | baccarat | pall-mall | tiparillo |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-2::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: gospel, electronic, dubstep
1. the fan of electronic is on the far left or far right##3
2. the fan of dubstep is in the middle##1
3. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the fan of gospel##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |   2   |   3   |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | dubstep | electronic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-3::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  bartender, nurse, social-worker
1. the social-worker is on the far left or far right##3
2. the social-worker is on the right of the bartender##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |  2   |  3   |
| Job   | nurse | bartender | social-worker |

 #################################

 
