.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-6::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: swimming, badminton, handball
1. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is badminton##3
2. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
3. the person who's sport is badminton is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3       |
| Sport   | swimming | badminton | handball |

